data.description: Home back on the market due to buyer not being able to finance. Welcome to 1528 Oldenburg Drive, a charming and spacious home located in the desirable neighborhood of Tupelo in Mount Pleasant. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a grand foyer that leads to an open and bright living area. The main level features a well-designed floor plan, boasting an open concept living area with a fireplace, a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, an at home office, and a main level half bath. All three bedrooms are upstairs including a large flex space. The primary bedroom is bright with natural light and the bathroom has a walk in shower and a large walk in closet. The home also features additional generously sized bedrooms, providing plenty of space. The fenced in backyardand newly added screened in porch is perfect for relaxing comfortably outside and entertaining your guests.   The neighborhood amenities include a community pool, playground, and walking trails, providing endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation. 1528 Oldenburg Drive is conveniently located in close proximity to Mount Pleasant's finest shopping, dining, and entertainment options. With easy access to major highways and just a short drive from the stunning beaches of Isle of Palms and Sullivan's Island, this home offers the perfect balance of suburban tranquility and urban convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Mount Pleasant living!
